    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Genus of biennial thistles native to Europe and Asia, naturalized throughout North America. They have dark green leaves and globular flower heads with prickly bracts. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
